<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en">
<head>
  <title>::: ChristmasFuture Email :::</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
  <style type="text/css">
  <!--
  html, body {
    margin:10px;
  }
  body {
    background: #FFF;
    font: 12px/16px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    text-align: left; /* this is asking IE to centre the container ;) */
  }
  h2 a {
    text-decoration:none;
    color: #360;
  }
  strong {
    color:#360;
  }
  -->
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div style="text-align:left;width:496px;margin:auto;">

<p>Hello <%=h @share.to_name? ? @share.to_name : @share.to_email %>,</p>

<p>Your friend, <a href="mailto:<%= @share.email %>"><%=h @share.name? ? @share.name : @share.email %></a> wanted to share their ChristmasFuture wishlist with you. Check out the projects below to learn more.</p>
 
<% if @share.e_card_id? && @share.e_card %><%= image_tag "http://#{@host}#{url_for_file_column(@share.e_card, "large")}", :alt => "" %><% end %>

<% if @share.message? %>
<p>Their message to you:</p>
<p><%=h @share.message %></p>
<% end %>

<hr />

<p>
  This year <a href="mailto:<%= @share.email %>"><%=h @share.name? ? @share.name : @share.email %></a> wants you to give them a new kind of gift through the ChristmasFuture website. A gift that helps eradicate extreme poverty. <strong>Here is their wishlist:</strong>
</p>

<hr />

<% if @projects && @projects.size > 0 %>
<% for project in @projects %>
  <h2><%= link_to project.name, dt_project_url(project) %></h2>

  <div class="projectRank">
    <% if project.target_start_date? %><span><strong>Target Start Date:</strong> <%= project.target_start_date.to_formatted_s(:long) %></span><% end %>
  </div>

  <p><strong>Project Description:</strong> <%= project.description %>&nbsp; &#8250; <%= link_to "Read more&hellip;", dt_project_url(project.id) %></p>

  <hr />
<% end %><% end %>

<p>Your friend is sharing a way that you can help change the world...for good.  <br />
<%= link_to (@share.project_id? && @share.project ? @share.project.name : 'ChristmasFuture Projects'), "http://" + @host + @url %></p>

<p>Thanks,<br />
<strong>The ChristmasFuture Team</strong></p>

</div>
</body>
</html>